{"data":{"doc":{"path":"/docs/dev-tools","title":"Dev tools","content":"<h1 id=\"dev-tools\"><a href=\"#dev-tools\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Dev tools</h1>\n<p>Tools for easier Gridsome development</p>\n<h2 id=\"eslint-plugin\"><a href=\"#eslint-plugin\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>ESLint plugin</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/eslint-plugin-gridsome\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.npmjs.com/package/eslint-plugin-gridsome</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"vetur\"><a href=\"#vetur\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Vetur</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=octref.vetur\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Vetur</a> is Vue tooling for VS Code.<br>\nVetur works perfect with Gridsome.</p>\n<h3 id=\"graphql-syntax-for-page-query-and-static-query\"><a href=\"#graphql-syntax-for-page-query-and-static-query\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>GraphQL syntax for <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;page-query&gt;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;static-query&gt;</code></h3>\n<p>Detail is <a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/vetur/issues/975#issuecomment-461197031\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>  </p>\n<ol>\n<li>Install <a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=kumar-harsh.graphql-for-vscode\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GraphQL</a></li>\n<li>Add this item in <code class=\"language-text\">settings.json</code></li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ... <span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"vetur.grammar.customBlocks\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"page-query\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"graphql\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"static-query\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"graphql\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  ...\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Run command <code class=\"language-text\">Vetur: Generate Grammar</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"autocompletion\"><a href=\"#autocompletion\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Autocompletion</h3>\n<p>Vetur has <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/gridsome-helper-json\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">gridsome-helper-json</a> since version 0.17.0\nhelper-json can autocomplete tag and attribute.\ngridsome-helper-json support <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;g-image&gt;</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;g-link&gt;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Pager&gt;</code>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1518 394' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-20'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-20)' width='1518' height='394' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAARCAYAAABtu6qMAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAACtElEQVRYw%2bVX227TQBD1lxTaJnF8j%2b3Y67tzbdomUFBFVSTECy888P%2bvpzNrx91EArWlFEgfjmZ3dlbJnJ09s9Z0K8TQHoPtr7CNYXtI0NTELCeC0VqztdvAQ0xeEmC6MXQzgOkJTEWNVVThIpmgDHOc0zyOSugHmHhHgOHE8nQdP4IfRxBBhmyUwCVCmpMPDhqSgIEZYjQWyOoCeTZFGdfIigVsP4M1SgmJYgnefw4lDy0UFXrDEcKkwPnVe6TrDdabG3z/9gOeWECUl0jrNUR1iURijXSy%2bTOoH4HHxrfIaF9C%2bTB4rllU6gPSAD9KkE8rhDlVwHwJkdaYr4iQcgHTFbReUpUUcOmK6Nb4edF1oe24QXNPSYhJjKVfwYDjVZ%2b1O%2bZ9hhTxaGeN99l0%2bgzOq9EAugI2aUDEGhAVKOucusAIH69vMVteUtIJwpj8kyUSIujNqYnjvoW3vefBcd/G0YlBBKfIypn8nayao6iXiJJK%2btiORSnH9Wwl/09WzlFNzxBnNUQ2gesLaXlfSnEcX07O4I8zGc/%2bU92hfH0iJsBJ39ntAgUlNyP1v6J